## Multi-Window Development
This window is for **CI/CD and DevOps**.
Workflow changes must consider impact on all services (Backend, NodeAgent, App, Admin).
Prefer reusable workflows and keep them maintainable across the organization.

## DoD Self-Check
- [ ] Linked to TASK-XXXX
- [ ] Reusable workflow created/updated where possible
- [ ] Impact on all dependent repositories evaluated